EECS494 p3.

This game need 3 players with (3) controllers.
We tested our game (only) using 3 PS4 controllers and did not test on Xbox controller.
Contact us if any issue related with input occurs.

Left Stick: Character movement
Right Stick: When sitting on a gear, adjust direction the corresponding object controlled by gear
Red Gear: Weapon Gear (Right stick to adjust direction, Press B (xbox) or O (ps4) to attack)
Blue Gear: Submarine Movement Gear (Right stick to move)
Green Gear: Shield Control Gear (Press B (in xbox) or O (in ps4) to open a bubble shield)


